---
/**
 * FAQSection Component
 * 
 * Displays frequently asked questions about the AppMRR leaderboard.
 * Includes information about:
 * - API key security
 * - Data update frequency
 * - Revenue calculation limitations
 * - How to delete an app
 * 
 * Uses HTML details/summary for collapsible Q&A items
 * 
 * Used in: index.astro
 */
---

<section class="faq-section">
        <div class="card faq-card">
                <div class="faq-header">
                        <span class="faq-badge">Need-to-know</span>
                        <h2>FAQ</h2>
                        <p class="faq-subtitle">Answers to common questions around security, data cadence, and removal.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-list">
                        <details>
                                <summary>Are my keys safe?</summary>
                                <p>
                                        We only require a RevenueCat API key with <strong>read-only</strong> access to "Chart metrics". Keys are encrypted at rest, never shared publicly, and can be revoked at any time within your RevenueCat dashboard.
                                </p>
                        </details>

                        <details>
                                <summary>How frequently is the data updated?</summary>
                                <p>
                                        Metrics refresh automatically every 24 hours (midnight UTC) so you always see the latest momentum without needing to manually trigger updates.
                                </p>
                        </details>

                        <details>
                                <summary>Why can't I see all-time revenue?</summary>
                                <p>
                                        RevenueCat currently exposes revenue for the last 28 days. We're exploring safe ways to display historical charts as soon as the data becomes available.
                                </p>
                        </details>

                        <details>
                                <summary>How do I remove my app?</summary>
                                <p>
                                        Revoke the API key from RevenueCat or contact our support email. The entry disappears automatically on the next daily sync (within 24 hours).
                                </p>
                        </details>
                </div>
        </div>
</section>

<style>
	.faq-section {
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

        .card {
                background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--card-bg) 94%, transparent);
                border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--card-border) 60%, transparent);
                border-radius: 22px;
                overflow: hidden;
                transition: background-color 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
                box-shadow: 0 30px 70px -50px color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 26%, transparent);
                backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
        }

        .faq-card {
                padding: clamp(1.35rem, 4vw, 2rem);
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .faq-header {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0.65rem;
        }

        .faq-badge {
                align-self: flex-start;
                padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
                border-radius: 999px;
                font-size: 0.75rem;
                font-weight: 600;
                letter-spacing: 0.08em;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--card-bg) 70%, transparent);
                border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--card-border) 70%, transparent);
                color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 80%, var(--muted) 20%);
        }

        .faq-header h2 {
                margin: 0;
                font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
                color: var(--fg);
        }

        .faq-subtitle {
                margin: 0;
                color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--muted) 65%, var(--fg) 35%);
                font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2.3vw, 1rem);
                line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .faq-list {
                display: grid;
                gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        .faq-list details {
                border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--card-border) 70%, transparent);
                border-radius: 16px;
                padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem;
                background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--card-bg) 85%, transparent);
                transition: border-color 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .faq-list details[open] {
                background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--row-hover) 60%, var(--card-bg) 40%);
                border-color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--card-border) 55%, transparent);
                box-shadow: 0 16px 32px -26px color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 28%, transparent);
        }

        .faq-list summary {
                cursor: pointer;
                font-weight: 600;
                color: var(--fg);
                list-style: none;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: space-between;
                gap: 1rem;
        }

        .faq-list summary::-webkit-details-marker {
                display: none;
        }

        .faq-list summary::after {
                content: "+";
                font-weight: 600;
                font-size: 1rem;
                color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--muted) 70%, var(--fg) 30%);
                transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .faq-list details[open] summary::after {
                transform: rotate(45deg);
        }

        .faq-list p {
                margin: 0.75rem 0 0 0;
                color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--muted) 70%, var(--fg) 30%);
                line-height: 1.7;
                font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
                .faq-section {
                        margin-top: 1.5rem;
                }

                .faq-card {
                        gap: 1.25rem;
                }

                .faq-list details {
                        padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
                }
        }
</style>

